**Running** | Attribute
__Basics__
If attacked at night by a wolfish player, a Running player will escape unharmed the first time, and be informed they were attacked.
A wolfish player who attacks a Running player will be informed of this, if the attack is a group they will be informed instead.
After being attacked once, it will lose its ability.

__Formalized__
Starting: Protect @Self from `Attacks` by @(Attr:Wolfish) through Passive Defense during Night (~UntilUse)
On Passive Defense:
  • Reveal `@Self is Running and ran away` to @AttackLocation
  • Reveal `You got attacked and ran away` to @Self
